headline: Amid Government Shutdown, Americans Ready To Turn to Self-Reliance, GoDaddy & HarrisX Poll Finds
summary: Majority of Americans and three-quarters of federal employees report financial anxiety, but half say they're ready to start a side hustle or small business if needed TEMPE, AZ / ACCESS Newswire / October 21, 2025 / Originally published by GoDaddy ...
